                            <comment id="13127914" author="hudson" created="Fri, 14 Oct 2011 22:15:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra-0.8 #374 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Cassandra-0.8/374/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Cassandra-0.8/374/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
